divs: sighting detailsi have photographed more "unknowns" over my home the past couple of months. i uploaded almost 50 new photos, from may & june, of some interesting "objects" at my home. the most recent, are in my photobucket album.....on pages 1 thru' 3....though i have 9 pages uploaded to date. the actual dates & times are on the copies of the originals of each photo...located in their lower right hand corners. i uploaded cropped, as well as auto-enhanced copies of each original as well, so you can see the objects in detail. what i find very interesting, is that it appears to be either the same object (or like objects) appearing on these different dates & times. when i am taking photos, i will see a very large shadowy darkness pass overhead, as well as brilliant flashes of light in the sky. i now have 159 photos, as well as 5 videos and 1 slideshow added, and i will be adding more to my photobucket album, as time allows. i have included cropped and auto-enhanced copies of the original photos here, in my photobucket album: http:\\s116.photobucket.com\albums\o31\mufonstarchild\ (copy & paste the above link into your searchbar) patty d mufon intl & michigan mufon field investigator
